" />"},{"pid":"21761c954fcfa7a88dbd4cf8faf57362895e55e5","tid":2104304,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"ceb3a569a5b3237e6ca78065672175b47fa341a6","tid":2104304,"uid":242805,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a0f2efb4031b586fd15b35150cd1d65f4d7ab28d","tid":2104304,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:11:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200712/6W2A4INRCHP74J2NWXZ73FELIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200712%2F6W2A4INRCHP74J2NWXZ73FELIQ%2F&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnpugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=323d95ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200712%2F6W2A4INRCHP74J2NWXZ73FELIQ%2F&h=1f4d95e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200712/6W2A4INRCHP74J2NWXZ73FELIQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n法律界：警查私隱案奇怪 <br />\n鍾劍華：我話特首辦洩資料 係咪搜佢電腦？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【夜搜民研】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法推行後，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n研究所副行政總裁鍾劍華直斥，行動明顯是政治打壓，政府做法「下作」、「低莊」。受警方搜查影響，研究所職員需通宵重新準備票站二維碼，令昨日的初選延遲三小時至中午才舉行。有法律界人士指，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n前晚6時許，約十名網罪科探員持搜查令到民研的黃竹坑總部，指懷疑包<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n發現涉案的2013年調查問卷或撿走電腦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fXbq_DEzr7uxJuh8Ue7jOlNcMew=/797x448/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZJG2P5TUO5IGVA6XPVUESIW5AA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfXbq_DEzr7uxJuh8Ue7jOlNcMew%3D%2F797x448%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZJG2P5TUO5IGVA6XPVUESIW5AA.gif&h=1823aded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾劍華（左）及民研主席鍾庭耀昨凌晨會見記者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n累重製二維碼延遲投票<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警查票站影市民 製白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n民研副行政總裁鍾劍華指，當日下午2時曾有人到民研的灣仔辦事處示威，而當晚警方到民研總部調查時，職員正為票站出入登記用的二維碼、票站指引等準備，但因警方搜查而延誤，加上有警員搜查過程中疑不小心